Feature <code>as</code> Syntax Angle-Bracket Syntax Syntax <code>value as Type</code> <code>&lt;Type&gt;value</code> JSX Compatibility ✅ Works in <code>.tsx</code> ❌ Not allowed in <code>.tsx</code> files Preferred Usage Always use <code>as</code> in React/JSX files Use angle-brackets in <code>.ts</code> files <pre><code>// ✅ Preferred in all contexts
let input = someValue as string;

// ❌ Will cause error in TSX files
let input = &lt;string&gt;someValue;
</code></pre>
